OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FThe trial was told that Brandt sent at
OL,7,Fleast 17 emails and three phone
OL,8,Fmessages to Ms Mordaunt, as well as
OL,9,Fturning up at her Portsmouth
OL,10,Fconstituency office out-of-hours
OL,11,Fbetween 11 September 2023 and 12 May
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FBrandt, who lived on the Isle of Wight
OL,15,Fat the time, failed to comply with the
OL,16,Fterms of a conditional caution issued
OL,17,Fin April 2024 which required him to
OL,18,Fcomplete a victim awareness course and
OL,19,Fnot to contact Dame Penny, the trial
OL,20,Fheard.
