OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FThe divorced father-of-two, who now
OL,7,Flives in Lymington, Hampshire, then
OL,8,Fleft two voicemail messages for her on
OL,9,F6 and 10 May and in one of the
OL,10,Fmessages, he said: "I am going to go
OL,11,Fon gently knocking at your door in
OL,12,Forder to shake your hand, I am not
OL,13,Fgiving up."
OL,15,FBrandt, who worked as a professional
OL,16,Fsailor, was also made subject to an
OL,17,Finterim stalking protection order at
OL,18,FIsle of Wight Magistrates' Court on 16
OL,19,FJuly 2024.
