OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FDame Penny said in a statement to
OL,7,Fpolice that she "feared sexual
OL,8,Fviolence" because of the defendant's
OL,9,F"creepy" behaviour.
OL,11,FBrandt wept and held his hands over
OL,12,Fhis face after the verdicts were
OL,13,Freturned by the jury.
OL,15,FJudge William Mousley KC adjourned the
OL,16,Fcase for a pre-sentence report to be
OL,17,Fprepared on Brandt and released him on
OL,18,Fconditional bail until the sentencing
OL,19,Fhearing on 16 January.
