OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FHe said: "You will be sentenced on
OL,7,FFriday 16 January, a pre-sentence
OL,8,Freport will be prepared by the
OL,9,FProbation Service."
OL,11,FClearly emotional at times, Dame Penny
OL,12,Ftold the court: "I have been a
OL,13,Fparliamentarian for 14 years and
OL,14,Fduring that time I have had to deal
OL,15,Fwith all kinds of threats and issues.
OL,17,F"It's different from your average
OL,18,Fcitizen, I am quite used to dealing
OL,19,Fwith this and I am quite a robust
OL,20,Findividual.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
