OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,F"The difference between this case and
OL,7,Feven threats to shoot me and my
OL,8,Ffamily, they are easier to deal with
OL,9,Fbecause that threat is not constantly
OL,10,Fpresent, it's not something you are
OL,11,Fhaving to think about every single day
OL,12,Fwhen you are leaving your house.
OL,14,F"I am not a professional, I do not
OL,15,Fhave counselling experience but I have
OL,16,Fa lot of life experience and dealing
OL,17,Fwith vulnerable people or people who
OL,18,Fare mentally unwell or strange in
OL,19,Fanother way, and I believe this man
OL,20,Fwas a real threat to me and still is."
