OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,FExplaining why he wanted to meet Dame
OL,7,FPenny, Brandt, a former councillor for
OL,8,FEast Hampshire District Council, told
OL,9,Fthe court: "I wanted to commiserate
OL,10,Fwith her for not getting the top job
OL,11,Fin the autumn, I think she would still
OL,12,Fhave been prime minister if she had
OL,13,Fbeen.
OL,15,F"I wanted to congratulate her because
OL,16,Fshe was a reforming leader of the
OL,17,FCommons, I wanted to congratulate her
OL,18,Fon the coronation, chat to her about
OL,19,Fher time in office, have her sign a
OL,20,Fcopy of her book.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
