OL,3,CEx-councillor found guilty of stalking
OL,4,CDame Penny Mordaunt
OL,6,F"It was entirely political and
OL,7,Fentirely harmless."
OL,9,FBrandt, who said that he had been
OL,10,Fdiagnosed as having ADHD and being on
OL,11,Fthe autism spectrum, said that he had
OL,12,Fnot had responses from Dame Penny's
OL,13,Foffice about his requests to meet her,
OL,14,Fand added: "I wasn't getting a reply,
OL,15,FI harmlessly kept trying."
